data.description: Located on a cul-de-sac this 2-story brick house features 4 bedrooms and 3 1/2 bathrooms. The Kitchen offers 2 pantries with additional breakfast bar area that was added. Downstairs features formal living room and a dining room. The laundry room also has a laundry chute. The owner suite located on the 1st floor is spacious with a walk-closet and the bathroom offers double sink vanity, separate shower & tub.  Secondary rooms are spacious as well. This home offers a large backyard with endless possibilities. Miramesa offers great amenities like play area for kids, swimming pool, splash pad, tennis court, and sand volleyball court.  Zoned to CFISD.
